01:13:40,782 --> 01:13:42,462
Jess, oprosti.

701
01:14:19,847 --> 01:14:22,985
Hej, samo...

702
01:14:24,011 --> 01:14:25,548
...smiri se.

703
01:14:27,131 --> 01:14:28,633
Smiri se!

704
01:14:32,286 --> 01:14:35,646
Što smo uradili? Nismo dio ovog
broda. Sad smo stigli.

705
01:14:35,647 --> 01:14:38,994
Lutali smo, nikog nije bilo.

706
01:14:38,995 --> 01:14:42,923
Mogu sad da odem.
Otici cu, samo...

707
01:14:42,924 --> 01:14:44,640
...smiri se.

708
01:14:45,164 --> 01:14:48,107
Smiri se, OK??

709
01:14:54,377 --> 01:14:55,675
Jess?

710
01:14:57,470 --> 01:14:58,990
Jess.

711
01:15:00,199 --> 01:15:03,541
Jess, što to radiš?
Što je ovo?

712
01:15:03,661 --> 01:15:05,790
Što je to na tebi?

713
01:15:05,910 --> 01:15:09,674
- Necu da mi vidiš lice.
- Zašto?

714
01:15:09,675 --> 01:15:12,065
Zato što ovo nisam ja.

715
01:15:12,137 --> 01:15:17,411
Ja sam negdje na preokrenutoj jahti
i ti si sa mnom.

716
01:15:17,412 --> 01:15:21,224
I nakon što te ubijem,
vratit cemo se.

717
01:15:21,225 --> 01:15:22,789
Stvarno?

718
01:15:24,736 --> 01:15:27,864
Znaš što? Zašto ne spustiš
prvo oružje?

719
01:15:27,865 --> 01:15:28,963
Dobro?

720
01:15:29,327 --> 01:15:30,607
Hajde.

721
01:15:30,883 --> 01:15:33,500
Vidiš, jahta ce se vratiti
kad svi budete bili mrtvi.

722
01:15:33,501 --> 01:15:35,832
Sve sam radila kao i prije,

723
01:15:35,833 --> 01:15:38,924
ali kad se bude jahta vratila,
bit cu spremna i chekat cu.

724
01:15:38,925 --> 01:15:42,845
Bit cu na mostu i nikoga necu pustiti
da se ukrca, ni drugu ja.

725
01:15:42,964 --> 01:15:45,473
Natjerat cu ih da svi ostanu
na prevrnutoj jahti.

726
01:15:45,474 --> 01:15:46,656
OK.

727
01:15:46,683 --> 01:15:50,643
Jess, uradit cemo sve što želiš.

728
01:15:50,807 --> 01:15:53,936
Dobro? Samo spusti oružje.

729
01:15:57,545 --> 01:15:59,855
- Hajde!
- Jako mi je žao.

730
01:15:59,856 --> 01:16:01,954
Ne, ne, ne!

731
01:16:03,332 --> 01:16:05,065
Greg!

732
01:16:05,087 --> 01:16:07,646
- Bože! - Greg!
- Pomogni mu!

733
01:16:07,647 --> 01:16:11,024
Pomogni mu! Ti prokleta kujo!
Ti si ga upucala!

734
01:16:11,025 --> 01:16:12,953
- Što?
- To je rekao, da si ga ti upucala!

735
01:16:12,954 --> 01:16:15,641
- Nisam ni bila sa Gregom!
- Mrtav je!

736
01:16:15,642 --> 01:16:17,597
Mrtav je!

737
01:16:17,891 --> 01:16:21,660
Bože, ti si prokleta luðakinja!

738
01:16:22,832 --> 01:16:25,196
Bože! Downey!

739
01:16:26,129 --> 01:16:27,507
Ne!

740
01:16:29,453 --> 01:16:31,613
Bože! Dušo!

741
01:17:40,108 --> 01:17:41,299
Molim te.

742
01:17:43,254 --> 01:17:44,845
Nemoj me ubiti!

743
01:17:44,863 --> 01:17:46,298
Imam sina.

744
01:17:47,414 --> 01:17:48,872
Imam sina.

745
01:18:55,066 --> 01:18:56,195
Dosta!

746
01:19:09,011 --> 01:19:10,353
Tko si ti?

747
01:19:11,917 --> 01:19:14,909
- Reci mi!
- Vratit ce se.

748
01:19:14,910 --> 01:19:16,155
Tko si ti?

749
01:19:16,221 --> 01:19:18,820
Vratit ce se. Moraš ih ubiti.

750
01:19:18,821 --> 01:19:20,348
To je jedini nachin da
se vratiš kuci.

751
01:19:20,349 --> 01:19:21,886
Što to jebeno govoriš?

752
01:19:21,887 --> 01:19:24,555
To je jedini nachin da
spasiš našeg sina.

753
01:19:24,556 --> 01:19:27,084
Moraš ih ubiti! Ubij ih!

754
01:19:27,085 --> 01:19:28,680
Ubij ih!

755
01:22:54,306 --> 01:22:57,215
Požuri dušo, zakasnit cemo.

756
01:23:32,588 --> 01:23:36,088
Koja je svrha da ti kupujem stvari?
Kad ih samo ostavljaš u dvorištu!

757
01:23:36,089 --> 01:23:39,114
Dosta mi je više da ti pricham!

758
01:23:39,115 --> 01:23:45,115
Necu ti više kupovati igrachke,
dok ne pochneš chuvati ove koje imaš!

759
01:23:48,267 --> 01:23:50,264
Što je sad?

760
01:23:54,294 --> 01:23:56,824
Samo da pochistim, zar ne?

761
01:23:59,709 --> 01:24:03,449
Samo da pochistim jebeni nered!

762
01:24:03,450 --> 01:24:05,441
Što je sa tobom?

763
01:24:05,477 --> 01:24:08,296
Što je sa tobom?! Ti, govno malo!

764
01:24:08,836 --> 01:24:14,416
Samo tražim jedan slobodan dan!
Samo jedan jebeni dan!

765
01:24:15,294 --> 01:24:19,107
Ne znam zašto ne možeš
crtati sliku kao normalno dijete.

766
01:24:19,108 --> 01:24:21,093
Sigurno si naslijedio od oca.

767
01:24:21,094 --> 01:24:23,579
I on je bio isto šupak!

768
01:24:37,769 --> 01:24:39,102
Sranje!

769
01:24:51,191 --> 01:24:52,320
Jack?

770
01:24:53,369 --> 01:24:56,614
Da li si vidio da je
netko zvonio na vrata?

771
01:25:32,720 --> 01:25:33,956
Tommy?

772
01:25:35,494 --> 01:25:37,404
Doði ovamo, dušo.

773
01:25:37,711 --> 01:25:39,301
Doði ovamo!

774
01:25:39,318 --> 01:25:42,468
Doði ovamo! Sve je u redu.

775
01:25:48,146 --> 01:25:50,296
Mama je dobro, vidiš?

776
01:25:52,324 --> 01:25:53,759
Mama je dobro .

777
01:25:56,625 --> 01:25:59,657
Samo si loše sanjao, to je sve.

778
01:25:59,658 --> 01:26:01,178
Ništa više.

779
01:26:02,627 --> 01:26:06,777
Stvari u lošem snu ne postoje.

780
01:26:52,195 --> 01:26:56,362
Od sad ce se promijeniti stvari, Tommy.

781
01:26:56,363 --> 01:26:58,958
Mama više nece izgubiti živce.

782
01:26:58,959 --> 01:27:02,343
chak i ako radiš pogrešno.

783
01:27:02,344 --> 01:27:04,399
I nece te povrijediti.

784
01:27:05,464 --> 01:27:07,720
Znam da te nece dirati.

785
01:27:07,721 --> 01:27:10,345
Znaš kako to znam, Tommy?

786
01:27:11,116 --> 01:27:15,129
Zato što je žena, koja ti je
to radila nije bila mama.

787
01:27:15,130 --> 01:27:16,729
Ovo je mama.

788
01:27:16,730 --> 01:27:18,677
Mama je dobra.

789
01:27:23,453 --> 01:27:25,186
Sranje!

790
01:27:37,427 --> 01:27:39,099
Otvori mama!

791
01:27:39,374 --> 01:27:41,573
Tommy, ostani u kolima.

792
01:27:41,574 --> 01:27:44,100
Mama ce je sahraniti, dobro?

793
01:28:45,285 --> 01:28:48,435
Moramo ici!
Moramo otici odavde!

794
01:28:52,841 --> 01:28:54,837
Prestani vikati dušo!

795
01:28:54,838 --> 01:28:57,036
- Molim te, Tommy. To je samo krv.
- Mama!

796
01:28:57,037 --> 01:28:59,664
- Mama!
- Ne vichi!

797
01:28:59,784 --> 01:29:02,340
Tommy, gledaj. Nestalo je

798
01:29:02,722 --> 01:29:05,107
- Vidiš? Nestalo je.
- Ne.

799
01:30:34,405 --> 01:30:35,961
Jesi li dobro?

800
01:30:42,150 --> 01:30:43,588
Tko si ti?

801
01:30:44,075 --> 01:30:45,786
Samo vozach.

802
01:30:52,798 --> 01:30:56,033
Nema svrhe spašavati djechaka.

803
01:30:56,034 --> 01:30:59,519
Nitko ništa ne može uraditi
da ga vrati.

804
01:31:02,840 --> 01:31:04,307
Mogu li te odbaciti?

805
01:31:09,480 --> 01:31:11,157
Da.

806
01:31:11,682 --> 01:31:13,627
Vozi me u luku!

807
01:31:37,144 --> 01:31:38,468
Hej.

808
01:31:43,525 --> 01:31:46,770
Ostavi taximetar da otkucava.

809
01:31:52,043 --> 01:31:54,048
Vratit ceš se, zar ne?

810
01:31:56,850 --> 01:31:59,376
Da, obecavam.

811
01:32:20,809 --> 01:32:22,003
Jess.

812
01:32:26,207 --> 01:32:27,687
Poznaješ me?

813
01:32:28,234 --> 01:32:33,383
Osjecam kao da znam.
Greg dosta pricha o tebi.

814
01:32:33,815 --> 01:32:37,155
- Gdje je Greg?
- Što misliš?

815
01:32:37,728 --> 01:32:40,113
Hajdemo, kasniš.

816
01:32:40,483 --> 01:32:44,341
- Ti imaš dijete, zar ne?
- Da.

817
01:32:44,342 --> 01:32:47,062
Zašto ga nisi povela?

818
01:32:53,650 --> 01:32:55,272
U školi je.

819
01:32:56,786 --> 01:32:58,351
Sigurno?

820
01:32:59,259 --> 01:33:00,733
Da.

821
01:33:11,398 --> 01:33:14,118
- Dobro je?
- Ne vjerujem.

822
01:33:15,286 --> 01:33:18,391
Bok. Što je bilo? Što se dogodilo?

823
01:33:21,106 --> 01:33:23,897
- Hej.
- Žao mi je.

824
01:33:24,404 --> 01:33:27,167
Nemaš se za što isprichavati.

825
01:33:27,168 --> 01:33:30,748
- Što je bilo?
- Samo sam umorna.

826
01:33:31,200 --> 01:33:33,500
Slušaj, ne moramo danas ici
ako ne želiš.

827
01:33:33,501 --> 01:33:36,302
Ne. Želim ici.

828
01:33:36,595 --> 01:33:37,973
Sigurno?

829
01:33:44,190 --> 01:33:45,478
Da.

830
01:33:46,295 --> 01:33:48,395
Da? Onda hajdemo!

831
01:33:54,370 --> 01:33:57,640
- Ovo je Sally, i njen muž Downey.
- Zdravo.

832
01:33:57,641 --> 01:33:59,974
Ona je Sallyna prijateljica,
Heather, on je Victor.

833
01:33:59,975 --> 01:34:01,930
Hajdemo na jedrenje!

834
01:34:02,737 --> 01:34:04,602
OK!

